choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for 7 days.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Here is the meal plan for seven days without dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios and cashews. It includes a variety of food groups to ensure you get all the nutrients your body needs.
Breakfast:
- Banana smoothie made with mangoes or peaches
- Oatmeal cooked in water or coconut milk
Lunch:
- Vegan sandwich with hummus, avocado and tomato slices on whole grain bread
- Chickpea salad with cucumbers, bell peppers and lemon juice
Dinner:
- Tofu stir fry made with vegetables like broccoli, carrots and snow peas
- Lentil soup
Snacks:
- Fruit platter of apples, oranges, bananas and grapes
- Roasted chickpeas
Beverages:
- Water, herbal tea and green tea
This meal plan is just a sample. You can adjust it to your preferences and availability of food items in the market.
